c: 4
v: 64
t: "And We did not send a Messenger except to be obeyed in accordance with the permission (i.e.,in accordance with the Book) of Allah. And if they (i.e.,the hypocrites), when they did wrong to their ownselves, had come to you, then they had invoked Allah’s forgiveness, and the Messenger had invoked forgiveness for them, indeed they would have found Allah Ever-Attentive, continuously Merciful"